## AI ROI Framework
### Measuring and Maximizing Returns on a $120M AI Investment Portfolio

@notes: The finding: the company has invested $120M in AI over 3 years. Only $28M (23%) can be traced to measurable business outcomes. The remaining $92M has no documented ROI. This is a measurement and governance problem.

